    .entry-details
      %h4.name
        %span.versionAdded>
          version added:
          %a{:href => "/version/1.0/"} 1.0
        jQuery(':submit')
      %p.desc
        %strong> Description:
        Selects all elements of type submit.
      .longdesc
        %p
          The
          %code :submit
          selector typically applies to button or input elements. Note that some browsers treat
          %code &lt;button&gt;
          element as
          %code type="default"
          implicitly while others (such as Internet Explorer) do not.
